	<heading>Java</heading>
	
	<p>Java is an <tt>interpreted</tt> <tt>statically typed</tt> <tt>object oriented</tt> programming language. It was designed as a language for <tt>cross platform</tt> application development.</p>

	<p>Java (generally) runs on top of the Java Virtual Machine which allows the same <tt>bytecode</tt> to run on multiple platforms. Other languages such as <tt>JRuby</tt> can also run on top of the JVM, which makes it an interesting platform for programming language development.</p>
	
